<paragraph id="B3A3C099EA54659B03DB9C8B5F6AFA1A" pageId="4" pageNumber="137">
<taxonomicName id="AD6939381BA2D47C57F15FE6AEF43FBC" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Polia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Polia costirufa" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="137" phylum="Nemertea" rank="species" species="costirufa">Polia costirufa</taxonomicName>
Draudt, 1950, Mitteilungen der 
<normalizedToken id="31F48B2CEF0D5F6BB5F52CD3A88BD089" originalValue="Münchner">Muenchner</normalizedToken>
Entomologischen Gesellschaft 40: 28, pl. 2, fig. 9, here designated.
</paragraph>
